NK014(pha)013:1564: gdugs cha phyed las yu ba phyed //
NK014(pha)013:1565: ces pa ltar cha phran phyed phyed du byed pa'am /
NK014(pha)013:1567: pad+ma'i dpangs cha phran gcig gi phyed rgya phubs kyi
NK014(pha)013:1568: lan kan phag tu 'gro bar byas nas ji tsam
NK014(pha)013:1569: song ba'i tshad kyi gdugs kyi yu ba mthong bar
NK014(pha)013:1571: chos kyi 'khor lo'i thad ka'i 'og bsil khang gi nang du cong dang /
NK014(pha)013:1574: dril bu rnams kyang 'dogs par bzhed do //
NK014(pha)013:1576: chos kyi 'khor lo gtso bo'i brda //
NK014(pha)013:1577: ri dwags 'khor gyi brda yin te //
NK014(pha)013:1578: cong ni nges don brda sgra yin //
NK014(pha)013:1579: gan+di drang don brda yin te //
NK014(pha)013:1580: rdor dril thabs dang shes rab brda //
NK014(pha)013:1582: de ltar rta babs kyi skor 'di la mkhas pa gzhan yang khang thog 'phang dmas pa'i skyon dang /
NK014(pha)013:1583: lcog gi mdzes cha las sgo mdun du rgyan med
NK014(pha)013:1584: pa mi mdzes par che bar 'dod pa dang rta
NK014(pha)013:1585: babs mdun du bslang ba'i sgo tshad gcig ma sogs
NK014(pha)013:1586: sgo'i har mi sgribs pa mthong nas /
NK014(pha)013:1587: sgom don gyi rta babs sgo tshad gsum mas khyab
NK014(pha)013:1588: pas gcig ma gsungs pa rnams bris cha kho nar
NK014(pha)013:1590: glang rgyab mig gsum ma rta babs kyi 'og tu
NK014(pha)013:1591: sgo'i rlung po sgribs byed kyi tshul du 'dod pa
NK014(pha)013:1592: sogs pheb ka ris kyi bshad pa sna tshogs byung
NK014(pha)013:1593: ba de dag / da phyin chad chu shing gi 'bras bu ltar snying po med par 'gyur zhing /
NK014(pha)013:1594: yang dag pa'i gzhung 'di la nges par 'brangs par 'gyur te /
NK014(pha)013:1595: bdag gi rje bla ma'i legs bshad 'di'i mthu las so //
NK014(pha)013:1598: rnga yab lhab lhub phreng ba yis //
NK014(pha)013:1599: nges par phyogs bcur 'khrigs par bya //
NK014(pha)013:1600: zhes gsungs pa ltar sngar so so'i skabs su smos pa rnams dang /
NK014(pha)013:1601: der ma zad bde 'dus rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs las /
NK014(pha)013:1602: ba dan 'phan dang rdo rje rin chen rgyal mtshan mdzes par bya /
NK014(pha)013:1604: snying po rol pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)013:1605: gdugs dang ba dan rgyal mtshan tshogs //
NK014(pha)013:1606: rdo rje rin chen mtshan pa dang //
NK014(pha)013:1608: gzhal yas khang dngos gzhi'i pu shu'i zur bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)013:1609: sgo'i bsil khang gi mdun gyi ka ba nang ma
NK014(pha)013:1610: gnyis kyi phyi mtshams kyi thad steng rnams su dar
NK014(pha)013:1611: lce'i sham bu dang bcas pa'i gdugs dkar po rdo
NK014(pha)013:1612: rje rin po che'i tog can /
NK014(pha)013:1613: yu ba cha chung phyed dang gsum yod pa re re ste /
NK014(pha)013:1614: gzhung gzhan las spre'u'i gzung bar bshad do //
NK014(pha)013:1615: thog gi pu shu'i kho ra khor yug dang /
NK014(pha)013:1616: rta babs kyi steng gi zur bzhi dang sgrom gyi
NK014(pha)013:1617: snam bu'i mtha' rnams su rin po che'i bum pa
NK014(pha)013:1618: la gnas pa'i rgyal mtshan dang ba dan sgreng ba'o
NK014(pha)013:1620: rin po che'i dbyug pa'i rtser tog gi gdan zlum
NK014(pha)013:1621: po'i steng 'og tu re kh+aa'i bang rim ci rigs
NK014(pha)013:1623: de'i steng gi dkyil du rin po che dang rdo
NK014(pha)013:1624: rje'i tog byas pa'i tog gi gdan dang dbyug pa'i
NK014(pha)013:1625: mtshams nas g.yas g.yon gyi phyogs su dril bu dang
NK014(pha)013:1626: bcas pa'i dar dpyangs sam 'phan ring btags pa rlung
NK014(pha)013:1627: gis bskyod pas sum 'khyog tu lding ba /
NK014(pha)013:1628: ba dan ni gzhan de dang 'dra ba la tog gi gdan mi dgos pa yin no //
NK014(pha)013:1629: gzhung gzhan las ni rgyal mtshan gyi tog srog chags kyi gzugs kyis byas pa 'dod pa'ang yod do //
NK014(pha)013:1630: gzhal yas khang dbus kyi rtse mo'i tog nas gser
NK014(pha)013:1631: gyi thi gu'i pu shu'i kha'i dbyug pa ring po
NK014(pha)013:1632: la bcings pa'i ba dan gyi mgul mtshams la dkris
NK014(pha)013:1633: nas rta babs kyi 'khor lo'i steng gi gdugs kyi
NK014(pha)013:1634: rtse mo'i bar du 'then pa la /
NK014(pha)013:1635: gser gyi dril bu rnga yab dang nyi zla'i rlung
NK014(pha)013:1636: bskyod can gyi tshar sgreng ba las sgra skad snyan
NK014(pha)013:1639: rta babs rnams kyi rtse mo la //
NK014(pha)013:1640: gser gyi dril bu 'bar ba dag /
NK014(pha)013:1641: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra yang sgrogs //
NK014(pha)013:1643: bde 'dus zhi ba'i thig chog las /
NK014(pha)013:1644: ba dan dril bu legs par brgyan //
NK014(pha)013:1648: gzhal yas de yi sgo bzhi na //
NK014(pha)013:1649: glang chen rnams kyi mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)013:1652: glang seng gnyis kyis mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)013:1653: zhes pa'i phyi ma ltar na /
NK014(pha)013:1655: sgo bzhi yi ni logs dag tu //
NK014(pha)013:1656: glang chen dang ni seng ge bri //
NK014(pha)013:1657: zhes sgo logs la bri bar bshad cing /
NK014(pha)013:1659: phyi rol sgo ba glang seng dang //
NK014(pha)013:1663: sgo khang nang gi rgyan dgu ni //
NK014(pha)013:1664: rmang na nyon mongs zil gyis gnon //
NK014(pha)013:1665: glang dang seng ge ngang pa dang //
NK014(pha)013:1666: stobs dang mi 'jigs tshad med do //
NK014(pha)013:1667: sa le'i shing gi tshal yin na //
NK014(pha)013:1668: bar na las rnams so sor 'byed //
NK014(pha)013:1669: ri dwags mi dang srang kham dang //
NK014(pha)013:1670: g.yo dang 'byed dang stobs pa ste //
NK014(pha)013:1671: blon po rin po che bzhin no //
NK014(pha)013:1672: steng na sdug bsngal dang du len //
NK014(pha)013:1673: klu dang chu srin ga ru da //
NK014(pha)013:1674: ye shes thugs rje'i phrin las te //
NK014(pha)013:1675: khyung gi klu rgyal blang ba bzhin //
NK014(pha)013:1677: slob dpon chen po pad+mas mdzad pa'i gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i sgom rim las kyang /
NK014(pha)013:1678: sgo khang mun nag grib sos brgyan pa la //
NK014(pha)013:1679: bya khyung chu srin klu phrug gsum //
NK014(pha)013:1680: dge sdig bya ra ri dwags shang shang gsum //
NK014(pha)013:1681: seng ge glang chen ngang pa gsum ste dgu pa tras sbrel ba /
NK014(pha)013:1682: zhes gsungs pas sgo khang nang gi sgo'i g.yas g.yon
NK014(pha)013:1683: du rim pa gsum du bgos pa'i smad du glang
NK014(pha)013:1684: seng ngang pa / bar du ri dwags sha ra b+han /
NK014(pha)013:1689: sgo'i steng gi dbus su bya khyung /
NK014(pha)013:1690: de dag pa tra ris sbrel zhing //
NK014(pha)013:1691: rgyab nas sa le'i ljon shing skye ba'i 'dab ma bar bar nas mthong ba'o //
NK014(pha)013:1693: dbang gi rtags bcu 'di ltar te //
NK014(pha)013:1694: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK014(pha)013:1695: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK014(pha)013:1696: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK014(pha)013:1697: snying po lnga ni ye shes dang //
NK014(pha)013:1698: chos mos rdzu 'phrul smon lam dang //
NK014(pha)013:1699: skye las tshe dang longs spyod dang //
NK014(pha)013:1700: sems la dbang ba'i go rim bzhin //
NK014(pha)013:1701: zhes pa'i stong tshar rnams su dbu rgyan sogs rtags bcu yang 'god do //
NK014(pha)013:1702: sgo rgyan gyi rgyan 'di dag rgya bal du bris
NK014(pha)013:1703: pa'i thang sku 'ga' zhig la'ang de bzhin snang ngo
NK014(pha)013:1704: // zhes mkhas mchog bu ston rin po ches gsungs /
NK014(pha)013:1705: kha cig dbang gi rtags bcu logs su 'god mi dgos te /
NK014(pha)013:1706: dang po bzhi dang phyag rgya sgo ba la bartsi'o //
NK014(pha)013:1707: rgyal mtshan dang gdugs ni sgo khang steng na'onga /
NK014(pha)013:1708: bza' btung ni 'dod yon lha mos so //
NK014(pha)013:1709: bum pa snying po lngas gdab ni /
NK014(pha)013:1710: rta babs kyi snam bu rnams la'o //
NK014(pha)013:1711: zhes gsungs te brtags par bya'o //
NK014(pha)013:1713: rin chen bdun ni 'di ltar te //
NK014(pha)013:1714: dbang ni 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)013:1715: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)013:1716: lha mo btsun mo rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)013:1717: sgo ba dmag dpon tshul dgu dang //
NK014(pha)013:1718: mngon shes blon po bya ra ba //
NK014(pha)013:1719: stobs bcu glang po rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)013:1720: rdzu 'phrul ri dwags rta yi tshul //
NK014(pha)013:1721: rdzas brgyad la ni 'di ltar te //
NK014(pha)013:1722: bdud 'joms mi nub rgyal mtshan dang //
NK014(pha)013:1723: thugs rje gdugs dang dpal be'u dang //
NK014(pha)013:1724: bdud rtsi bum pa mi bsnyel rta //
NK014(pha)013:1727: zhes gsungs pa'i rin chen bdun dang /
NK014(pha)013:1728: rdzas brgyad kyang gong ma dag logs su 'god mi dgos par bzhed de /
NK014(pha)013:1729: gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i sgom rim las kyang /
NK014(pha)013:1730: rin chen bdun dang bkra shis brgyad //
NK014(pha)013:1731: dbang bcu de la don gyi rdzogs pas /
NK014(pha)013:1732: zhes gsungs pa'i dgongs pa yin no snyam mo //
NK014(pha)013:1733: 'on kyang gzhan du 'byung ba ltar bkod na'ang mi 'gal lam snyam ste /
NK014(pha)013:1734: de'i phyir spyi dang bstun na 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa ser po /
NK014(pha)013:1735: glang chen mche ba drug pa dkar po /
NK014(pha)013:1738: nor bu zur brgyad pa sngon po /
NK014(pha)013:1740: dmag dpon nag po rnams phyi rol dpag bsam shing la gnas par bya'o //
NK014(pha)013:1741: rdzas brgyad ni rta babs kyi ngos gnyis su re re 'god do //
NK014(pha)013:1742: shar du dpal be'u dang 'khor lo /
NK014(pha)013:1744: nub tu gdugs dang bum pa /
NK014(pha)013:1746: de dag ni slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK014(pha)013:1747: bas chos don du gsungs pa'i sgo rgyan te ma
NK014(pha)013:1748: grub na / 'dir med du mi rung ba'i rgyan ni /
NK014(pha)013:1749: sgo nang gi rgyan glang seng tsam bri /
NK014(pha)013:1751: sgo'i g.yas g.yon gnyis na t+aa la'i ljon shing re re dang /
NK014(pha)013:1752: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing yang re re ste /
NK014(pha)013:1753: de rnams gser gyi thi gus sbrel ba la /
NK014(pha)013:1754: dril bu dang g.yer kha 'phyang ba /
NK014(pha)013:1755: shing de dag la khu byug sogs byas brgyan pa dang /
NK014(pha)013:1756: khrus rdzing khrus kyi lha mos mdzes pa dang /
NK014(pha)013:1757: phyogs bzhi na rin po che'i phung po 'od 'bar ba gnyis gnyis te brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK014(pha)013:1758: de ltar yang rngam glog las /
NK014(pha)013:1759: sgo drung de dag re re na //
NK014(pha)013:1760: t+aa la'i ljon shing cong cong sbrel //
NK014(pha)013:1761: dri dang gzugs dang 'od dang ldan //
NK014(pha)013:1762: t+aa la'i skye shing de dag la //
NK014(pha)013:1763: khu byug la sogs bkra shis pa'i //
NK014(pha)013:1764: bya rnams snyan pa'i skad kyang sgrogs //
NK014(pha)013:1765: sgo drung de dag re re na //
NK014(pha)013:1766: khrus kyi rdzing bu dbyibs legs pa //
NK014(pha)013:1767: bro mchog yan lag brgyad ldan chu //
NK014(pha)013:1768: grangs med de dag re re na //
NK014(pha)013:1769: lha dang lha mo bsam mi khyab //
NK014(pha)013:1772: t+aa la'i ljon shing rang bzhin gnas //
NK014(pha)013:1773: dpag bsam shing gi rin chen 'bar //
NK014(pha)013:1774: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)013:1777: bden pa gsum pa'i ngang las dus gsum du skye
NK014(pha)013:1778: ba med pa'i phyir t+aa la zung bzhis brgyan pa'o
NK014(pha)013:1779: // re ba skong phyir rin chen phung po brgyad kyis bskor ba ste /
NK014(pha)013:1782: sgo bzhi g.yas g.yon ljon shing dang //
NK014(pha)013:1783: dpag bsam shing zung cong cong sbrel //
NK014(pha)013:1784: dril bu g.yer kha theg chen sgrogs //
NK014(pha)013:1785: bkra shis bya snyan sgra sgrogs ldan //
NK014(pha)013:1786: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad bskor ba //
NK014(pha)013:1787: rin chen phung po bzhi gnyis ldan //
NK014(pha)013:1789: 'di dag bsgom bya tsam du ma zad nges par bri dgos te /
NK014(pha)013:1791: rin chen sa gzhi skye shing dang //
NK014(pha)013:1792: rdzing bu dril bu g.yer khas spras //
NK014(pha)013:1793: rtag tu bri zhing bsgom par bya //
NK014(pha)013:1796: 'khor gyi gtso bos yongs bskul ba'i //
NK014(pha)013:1797: mchog gsum lha sogs rnams mang po //
NK014(pha)013:1798: rgyan dang mchod pa ldan par bri //
NK014(pha)013:1801: lha chen phyogs skyong brgyad kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)013:1807: sogs khong nas phyogs skyong ba brgyad sogs lha chen po rnams kyang 'god par gsungs shing /
NK014(pha)013:1808: sgro phug pa'i dngos slob kha rag sro snying gi 'grel par /
NK014(pha)013:1809: thams cad du ni dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK014(pha)013:1810: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)013:1811: zhes pas gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol na ma h+aa de wa la sogs lha chen brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)013:1812: nor rgyal la sogs klu chen brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)013:1813: nyi ma la sogs gza' chen brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)013:1814: smin drug la sogs pa rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK014(pha)013:1815: zhes lha klu gza' skar sogs kyang dgod par bzhed cing /
NK014(pha)013:1816: de rnams gang du 'god pa'i sa sngar bshad grub bo //
NK014(pha)013:1817: 'di dag sgyu 'phrul zhi dkyil gyi gzhal yas khang gi rnam bzhag che long tsam brjod pa ste /
NK014(pha)013:1818: 'di dag la dpags te khro dkyil khyams gnyis pa lta bu'i thog phub ni /
NK014(pha)013:1819: bar khyams phyi ma seng gdung ngam ka bas btegs
NK014(pha)013:1820: pa'i g.yab sgor gru bzhi pa'i tshul du phubs pa'i
NK014(pha)013:1821: khyams nang du / rin chen gar dgu stegs bu
NK014(pha)013:1822: gru bzhi pa dpangs cha phran bcu gcig pa la
NK014(pha)013:1823: gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i phyed tshad kyi rtsig
NK014(pha)013:1824: pa sgo sgo khyud la sogs pa byas pa'i gzhal
NK014(pha)013:1825: yas khang nang ma phyi ma las cha chen gcig
NK014(pha)013:1826: tsam gyis phyi nas bltas na mtho ba /
NK014(pha)013:1827: yangs pa zhig byas pa'i thog 'bubs rim pa gsum
NK014(pha)013:1828: sogs zhi ba ltar las nang sgo la rta babs
NK014(pha)013:1829: med pa'i phyir / de 'degs byed ka ba sogs
NK014(pha)013:1830: kyang mi dgos pas sgo'i ya phubs kyi rtsig pa'i
NK014(pha)013:1831: steng bar 'khor mo pha gu sogs gzhal yas dngos
NK014(pha)013:1837: thod pa sna lnga sna gsum dang //
NK014(pha)013:1838: thod skam rtsig pa rim pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)013:1839: tshangs dang lha dbang la brten pa //
NK014(pha)013:1840: mchog chen brgyad ka yin par 'dod //
NK014(pha)013:1841: lhag ma rnams ni thog phubs te //
NK014(pha)013:1842: gza' brgyad nyi zla'i glo skar ldan //
NK014(pha)013:1843: sbrul dang thod pa'i phreng ba nyid //
NK014(pha)013:1844: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed rnam par spras //
NK014(pha)013:1845: phyi nang rgyu 'bras gdug pa dag /
NK014(pha)013:1846: 'dul phyir rta babs bzhir bshad do //
NK014(pha)013:1847: sor phreng thod pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK014(pha)013:1848: dbang po nyi zla'i phreng bas spras //
NK014(pha)013:1849: khro bo sha lnga bdud rtsi dang //
NK014(pha)013:1851: dur khrod sa gzhi khrag dang bcas //
NK014(pha)013:1852: skyes bu gsal zhing phyogs mtshams brgyan //
NK014(pha)013:1854: thod tshal brgyus pa dur khrod rlung //
NK014(pha)013:1856: zhing 'phan phyogs mtshams brgyad dang ldan //
NK014(pha)013:1857: lha chen thod pa sbubs steng na //
NK014(pha)013:1859: he ru ka yi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK014(pha)013:1860: ma lus bri zhing bsgom par bya //
NK014(pha)013:1861: zhes gsungs pas gzhan rnams go sla la /
NK014(pha)013:1863: phyi ma thod pa sna lnga dang /
NK014(pha)013:1864: nang ma skam rlon rnying gsum gyis brtsigs shing /
NK014(pha)013:1865: khyams las gru chad stegs bu'i rnam par thod skam gyi rtsig pas 'phags pa'o //
NK014(pha)013:1868: de re re la snam phran brgyad brgyad do //
NK014(pha)013:1870: zhes pas phyi nang gi theg brgyad mtshon pa'i rgyu'i rta babs dang /
NK014(pha)013:1871: de'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu'i rta babs gnyis so //
NK014(pha)013:1872: 'dir dkyil 'khor nang ma stegs bu la gnas pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)013:1873: de la 'dzegs pa'i them skas kyang 'dzug dgos par mngon no //
NK014(pha)013:1874: de lta bus mtshon nas sgyu 'phrul bla ma las gsungs pa ltar /
NK014(pha)013:1875: spor ma'i sa spar te sgo brag rim pa gsum du bya ba 'am /
NK014(pha)013:1876: yang tshogs chen 'dus pa lta bu sgo sbrag shin
NK014(pha)013:1877: tu mang ba la'ang sbyar bas khang brtsegs mchod rten
NK014(pha)013:1878: gyi bang rim 'dra ba shin tu mdzes pa zhig
NK014(pha)013:1879: 'byung ngo // yang bka' brgyad lta bu gzhal yas
NK014(pha)013:1880: khang gcig gi nang du pho brang dgu rdzogs sogs
NK014(pha)013:1882: khyams cha phran gsum gyi cha g.yab gru bzhi pa'i
NK014(pha)013:1883: tshul du phubs pa'i gru chad dang khyams kyi mtshams
NK014(pha)013:1884: tshangs thig nas gru chad kyi mtha' thig bar cha
NK014(pha)013:1885: gsum du bgos pa'i sum cha nang ma'i phyi mtshams
NK014(pha)013:1886: su ka ba re re ste brgyad btsugs pa'i steng
NK014(pha)013:1887: du gdung ka ba gru bzhi pas bkab /
NK014(pha)013:1888: de'i khar tal bzhi mig mang ris su bris te 'bubs so //
NK014(pha)013:1889: 'dir bsgom bya la tal gdung bzhi'i 'og tu yod
NK014(pha)013:1890: pa'i gru bzhi pa de a long gru bzhi pa
NK014(pha)013:1891: lta bu yin pa'i phyir zur bzhir 'degs byed kyi
NK014(pha)013:1892: ka ba yin dgos gsung yang 'di lta bu'i bkod
NK014(pha)013:1893: pa bzo ba'i dus 'di ltar byas na brtan zhing
NK014(pha)013:1895: gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i bsgom rim las /
NK014(pha)013:1896: nang ka bzhi zhing tram bzhi la byas pa /
NK014(pha)013:1898: rgyal sras sman lung pa chen pos phyag len du btab pa mthong bas kyang /
NK014(pha)013:1899: gdung bzhi mig mang ris phub pa'i dbus kyi bsnol mtshams su ka ba re btsugs 'dug ste /
NK014(pha)013:1900: gzhal yas khang gi bkod pa shin tu che ba
NK014(pha)013:1901: bzhengs pa la de lta bu nges par dgos so
NK014(pha)013:1902: // yang gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i bsgom rim las /
NK014(pha)013:1903: chos sku kun la khyab brdal mtha' brgyad rang dag gi brdar /
NK014(pha)013:1904: bum pa sul brgyad pa bre dang bcas /
NK014(pha)013:1905: zhes gsungs pa ltar na shing brtsegs ji ltar rigs
NK014(pha)013:1906: pas btegs pa'i gdung brgyad phyogs bzhi zur bzhir btang
NK014(pha)013:1907: la phub ste / bum pa zur brgyad logs brgyad
NK014(pha)013:1908: pa zhig bya ste mchod rten gyi bya 'dab 'geb
NK014(pha)013:1909: la phub ste / pa dang / gdung zlum btang
NK014(pha)013:1910: ba sogs lag len la shin tu bde ba zhig
NK014(pha)013:1911: la phub ste / pa dang / byar yod do
NK014(pha)013:1912: // gzhan yang rta babs sgo tshad gsum ma lta
NK014(pha)013:1913: la phub ste / pa dang / byar yod do
NK014(pha)013:1914: // bu la / rtsig pa'i dpangs cha chen bzhi
NK014(pha)013:1915: dang sgo khang gi rtsig pa la cha chen gsum
NK014(pha)013:1917: rta babs sgo tshad gcig ma la rtsig dpangs cha chen gnyis dang cha phran gsum /
NK014(pha)013:1918: sgo phan chad de las cha phran gcig gis dma' ba'o //
NK014(pha)013:1919: 'bring tshad ni 'di nyid du sngar bshad pa ltar ro //
NK014(pha)013:1920: de ltar na rtsig dpangs mtho ba'i phyogs la rtsig pa rang la nang gi rgya phyed dpangs /
NK014(pha)013:1921: 'bring la gser gdung man chad la /
NK014(pha)013:1922: dma' ba la thog gi 'thug rngam man chad la rgya phyed dpangs yod do //
NK014(pha)013:1923: de bas na skabs thob brtsi dgos kyi /
NK014(pha)013:1924: phyogs gcig kho nar nges bzung byed pa la shes byed med cing /
NK014(pha)013:1926: gang ltar yang phyi dbyibs ni /
NK014(pha)013:1932: phyi dbyibs mchod rten mkhar thabs dang //
NK014(pha)013:1933: rgyal khab ri bo gur du 'dod //
NK014(pha)013:1936: dbyibs ni mchod rten ris mkhar thabs //
NK014(pha)013:1937: gur dang rgyal khab 'dra ba yin //
NK014(pha)013:1940: dang po mchod rten gyi dbyibs byed lugs la'ang dgongs pa mi mthun pa gnyis te /
NK014(pha)013:1941: snga rabs kyi bla ma phal che ba ni /
NK014(pha)013:1942: gzhal yas khang dngos gzhi'i pu shu man chad mchod rten gyi rmang lta bur byas la /
NK014(pha)013:1943: de'i steng du byang chen sogs mchod rten gyi dbyibs gang bde bya ba bzhed /
NK014(pha)013:1944: gsang rdzogs las gsungs pa ltar nyang ston chen po'i phyag len du btab pa'i lugs ni /
NK014(pha)013:1947: pho brang rnams phyi nas nang du rim par cha
NK014(pha)013:1948: chen gcig nas bzhi'i bar 'phags pa'i bang rim bzhi'i
NK014(pha)013:1949: rnam pa can gyi steng du /
NK014(pha)013:1952: bre sogs byas te byang chen rmang med pa lta bu'i phyogs bzhir /
NK014(pha)013:1953: rta babs bzhi yang ka ba cha chen gsum pas btegs nas /
NK014(pha)013:1954: sgo'i steng nas yar mchod rten gyi rnam par byas te /
NK014(pha)013:1955: phyi dbyibs mchod rten rtse lnga pa'i rnam par bzhed do //
NK014(pha)013:1957: kha cig steng khang gru bzhi pa la dgongs par 'chad pa mi rigs gsungs so //
NK014(pha)013:1959: bdud dpung 'joms pa'i dag par gsungs pa'i rdzong gi rnam pa'o //
NK014(pha)013:1961: de tsam las bya thabs zhib par ma gsungs na'ang /
NK014(pha)013:1962: 'os med kyi rigs pas 'di ltar grub ste /
NK014(pha)013:1963: 'jam dpal phyag rgya zil gnon las /
NK014(pha)013:1964: e yi pho brang zla gam gsum thod pa'i mkhar
NK014(pha)013:1965: bzhi 'khor lo brgyad lcags mkhar bcu gnyis bar khyams
NK014(pha)013:1966: bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs brgyad dang ldan 'obs chen
NK014(pha)013:1967: bcu drug rdo rje'i gur byas pa med par lhun
NK014(pha)013:1968: gyis grub bshig pa med par ngang gi stong zhes
NK014(pha)013:1969: gsungs pas / dkyil 'khor gyi mthar 'obs bcu drug dang /
NK014(pha)013:1970: de bsrung mi 'obs bsrung chen po bcu drug sogs gsungs pas /
NK014(pha)013:1971: rdzong gi sgra durga zhes pas bgrod dka' ba'i don yin pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)013:1973: de las gzhan du rdzong gi rnam pa bzo tshul 'tshol dgos na ha cang thal lo //
NK014(pha)013:1974: gsum pa rgyal khab kyi rnam pa ni /
NK014(pha)013:1975: rgya gar gyi rgyal po'i khab kyi khang bzang gi rnam pa ste /
NK014(pha)013:1976: rgya phub 'jig rten gyi lugs dang mthun par byas pa'i khang pa brtsegs pa'o //
NK014(pha)013:1977: bzhi pa gur gyi rnam pa ni /
NK014(pha)013:1978: dbus mtho ba'i phur bu zlum po rgya gur rnam pa ste /
NK014(pha)013:1979: dbus gdung zlum la btsugs nas 'bubs tshul bum pa zlum po dang gnad gcig go //
NK014(pha)013:1980: phyi dbyibs ji ltar byed kyang rtse mor rdo rje
NK014(pha)013:1981: rin po che'i tog ni nges par bya dgos te
NK014(pha)013:1982: / thams cad bshad pa mi langs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)013:1985: rgyud sde gong 'og rnams nas dkyil 'khor bkod pa
NK014(pha)013:1986: gcig tu ma nges pa du ma zhig 'byung ste
NK014(pha)013:1987: / so so'i rgyud 'grel sgrub thabs dang /
NK014(pha)013:1988: rdo rje slob dpon gyi gsung ngag las sogs dgos pa nyid do //
NK014(pha)013:1989: rgyal ba'i pho brang nyams dga' bar //
NK014(pha)013:1990: rgyal ba nyid kyis gsungs pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)013:1991: rgyal sras rnams kyis bkral ba'i don //
NK014(pha)013:1992: rgyal mchog gter chen chos kyi rje'i //
NK014(pha)013:1993: gsung las cung zad zin pa rnams //
NK014(pha)013:1995: d+aa ri dra ba de yis sbyar //
NK014(pha)013:1996: nyes kun mkhas la bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)013:1997: legs bshad gang mchis dge ba des //
NK014(pha)013:1998: rje btsun bla ma'i zhabs brtan cing //
NK014(pha)013:1999: mkha' khyab 'gro kun phyam gcig par //
NK014(pha)013:2000: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid gyur cig //
NK014(pha)013:2001: ces khro bo'i lo nag pa zla ba'i mar ngo'i
NK014(pha)013:2002: dus tshes bcu'i nyin o rgyan smin grol gling gi
NK014(pha)013:2003: chos grwar sug bris su sbyar ba'o //
